{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the default theme any app should use, and can be subclassed to define for example themes dedicated to countries. The "},{"code":"InverseTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is based on it.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It embeds also in its target the brand colors which are not shared nor exposed in lower level targets or outside any module not depending to it.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In other words, this ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" is based on the abstract "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":", uses all the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" kit and brings the Orange brand colors and assets."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"How to use the theme","anchor":"How-to-use-the-theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"text":" directly. To use the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" without further modifications, you will have to use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" for your root view and give it an instance of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Keep in mind the themes are "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift class objects","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" and can be heavy, so you may use only as instance as singleton and not store any properties."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSThemeOrange \/\/ To get OrangeTheme","import SwiftUI","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, in your views, you can simply use the theme through an environment variable to get the tokens:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get the theme environment variable","import SwiftUI","","struct SomeView: View {","","    \/\/ Get OUDS environment variable for theme thanks to themeable view","    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme","    ","    var body: some View {","        ","        \/\/ Use the theme to retrieve the tokens","        \/\/ For spaces: theme.spaces","        \/\/ For sizes: theme.sizes","        \/\/ For borders: theme.borders","        \/\/ For elevations: theme.elevations","        \/\/ For opacities: theme.opacities","        \/\/ For colors: theme.colors","    }","}",""],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"heading","text":"How to enrich the theme","anchor":"How-to-enrich-the-theme","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can enrich the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"text":" by subclassing it or by overriding some tokens.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"By-subclassing","level":3,"text":"By subclassing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You may want to define your own theme, thus you can override the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"text":" with your own class or just override the providers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You will have to consider the tokens provider you need:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"spaces tokens are ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"sizes tokens are in "},{"code":"OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"colors tokens are all defined in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"borders tokens are in ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"elevations tokens are in "},{"code":"OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"opacity tokens are in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"grid tokens are in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font tokens are in "},{"code":"OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ To use component tokens if needed","import OUDSTokensSemantic \/\/ To use semantic tokens if needed","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ To use raw tokens if needed","","\/\/ MAKR: - For semantic tokens","","\/\/ Token provider for spaces","","class YourAppThemeSpaceTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var spaceFixedMedium: SpaceSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension400","    }","    override var spaceScaledShort: MultipleSpaceSemanticTokens {","        MultipleSpaceSemanticTokens(compact: spaceFixedJumbo, regular: spaceFixedJumbo)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for sizes","","class YourAppThemeSizeTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var sizeIconDecorative2xl: SizeSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension300","    }","    override var sizeIconDecorativeMd: SizeSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension900","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for colors","","class YourAppThemeColorTokensProvider: OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var colorBgSecondary: MultipleColorSemanticTokens {","        MultipleColorSemanticTokens(light: ColorRawTokens.colorDecorativeAmber500, dark: OrangeBrandColorRawTokens.colorOrange900)","    }","    override var colorActionEnabled: MultipleColorSemanticTokens {","        MultipleColorSemanticTokens(light: ColorRawTokens.colorDecorativeShockingPink100, dark: ColorRawTokens.colorFunctionalScarlet600)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for border","","class YourAppThemeBorderTokensProvider: OUDSBorderSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var borderStyleDefault: BorderStyleSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderStyleDashed","    }","    override var borderWidthMedium: BorderWidthSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderWidth100","    }","    override var borderRadiusTall: BorderRadiusSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderRadius800","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for elevation","","class YourAppThemeElevationTokensProvider: OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var elevationStickyEmphasized: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken {","        ElevationCompositeSemanticToken(ElevationRawTokens.elevationBottom_4_600)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for opacity","","class YourAppThemeOpacityTokensProvider: OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider {","    override var opacityStrong: OpacitySemanticToken {","        OpacityRawTokens.opacity920","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for grid","","class YourAppThemeGridTokensProvider: OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var gridExtraCompactColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","    override var gridCompactColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","    override var gridRegularColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for font","","class YourAppThemeFontTokensProvider: OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var typeDisplayLarge: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens {","        MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(compact: FontRawTokens.typeRegular150, regular: FontRawTokens.typeRegular150)","    }","    override var typeCodeMedium: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens {","        MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(FontRawTokens.typeBold300)","    }","}","","\/\/ MARK: - And also for components tokens","","class YourAppThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider {","    override public var buttonSizeMaxHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","    override public var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthThicker }","    override public var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.borderRadiusMedium }","    override public var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    override public var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ Etc."]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then define your own theme class and assign the providers, but beware, do not forget some providers as it will crash:"}]},{"code":["import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To get OrangeTheme","","\/\/ Define your theme","class YourAppTheme: OrangeTheme {","    ","    override init() {","        let providers: TokensProviders = [","            YourAppThemeColorTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeBorderTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeElevationTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeFontTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeGridTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeOpacityTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeSizeTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeSpaceTokensProvider(),","            YourAppThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(),","            \/\/ Etc.","        ]","","        super.init(tokensProviders: providers)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then add the theme:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["import OUDS  \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: YourAppTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"level":3,"anchor":"By-overriding","type":"heading","text":"By overriding"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Quite simple and similar to the previous solution, but give only the providers to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"But beware, in all cases if will crash is some providers are missing.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Ensure you add ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"all"}]},{"type":"text","text":" the expected providers. You can mix your own providers and those from Orange theme."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: ","                OrangeTheme(tokensProviders: ...)) { ","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"role":"collection","roleHeading":"Framework","externalID":"OUDSThemesOrange","symbolKind":"module","title":"OUDSThemesOrange"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Group","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"],"title":"Group"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSeman